## 2. Implemention of the code
--- 
The dependiences include:
```
-- Pytorch
-- Numpy
-- Sklearn
-- Scipy
```

The default input path is `./input/ata_EEG_AI.mat` , to change to another input path, please modify the first line of the second cell of the notebook:
```
EEG_PATH = './input/data_EEG_AI.mat'
```
If the input data shape is different from (24, 801, 7800), please modify the related terms in the second cell:
```
n_samples = 7800 # number of total sample
n_letters = 300 # number of samples for a single letter
n_ch = 24 # number of channels in a sample
n_time = 801 # number of time points in a sample
```
